  15 Jan 2008; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.3.ebuild:
  Mark 0.2.3 stable on X86, tested with a Zen Sleek on 2.x firmware.

  20 Dec 2007; Ferris McCormick <fmccor@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.3.ebuild:
  sparc stable, 30-day bookkeeping and allow unmasking its package.use.mask on
  sparc.

*libmtp-0.2.4 (19 Dec 2007)

  19 Dec 2007; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +libmtp-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Version bump, as requested by Cristian "majeru" Magherusan on IRC.

  01 Dec 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  20 Nov 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.3.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc

  13 Nov 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.3.ebuild:
  Add ~alpha

  13 Nov 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.3.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa for audacious-plugins (mr_bones).

*libmtp-0.2.3 (26 Oct 2007)

  26 Oct 2007; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> libmtp-0.2.1.ebuild,
  +libmtp-0.2.3.ebuild:
  Bumped to 0.2.3 as requested by Cristian "majeru" Magherusan on IRC. Marked
  0.2.1 stable on X86, tested on a ThinkPad X41 using a Zen Sleek.

